ZH: 他因为抢劫被判入监狱十年。
EN: He was sentenced to ten years in prison for robbery.

ZH: 这座监狱有很高的墙壁，很难逃跑。
EN: The prison has high walls that make it difficult to escape.

ZH: 我的弟弟正在监狱服刑。
EN: My younger brother is serving his sentence in prison.

ZH: 他是个危险的罪犯，应该被关进监狱。
EN: He is a dangerous criminal who should be locked up in prison.

ZH: 这座监狱设有高度安保和监控系统。
EN: This prison is equipped with high-security measures and surveillance systems.

ZH: 我们应该为重刑犯建立更好的监狱制度。
EN: We should establish better prison systems for serious offenders.

ZH: 这个城市的监狱已经超过了最大容纳量。
EN: The city's prisons have exceeded their maximum capacity.

ZH: 监狱里的人们都渴望重获自由。
EN: People in prison long for freedom.

ZH: 据说这座监狱是最严密的监狱之一。
EN: It is said that this prison is one of the most secure prisons.

ZH: 我们应该对待囚犯，给予他们改过自新的机会。
EN: We should treat prisoners and give them a chance to reform.

ZH: 每年有很多罪犯重新融入社会，成功避免再次入狱。
EN: Many criminals successfully reintegrate into society each year and avoid returning to prison.

ZH: 这个监狱提供各种职业培训课程，以帮助囚犯重建生活。
EN: This prison offers various vocational training programs to help inmates rebuild their lives.

ZH: 这个囚犯已在监狱里度过了十年的刑期。
EN: This inmate has spent ten years of his sentence in prison.

ZH: 警察在附近的监狱周围加强了安保措施。
EN: The police have increased security measures around the nearby prison.

ZH: 许多罪犯通过学习在监狱里获得了新的技能。
EN: Many criminals acquire new skills through education in prison.

ZH: 这个监狱里有各种各样的犯罪分子。
EN: This prison houses a wide range of criminals.

ZH: 有些人认为监狱应该更注重惩罚，而不是改造。
EN: Some people believe that prisons should focus more on punishment rather than rehabilitation.

ZH: 这个囚犯感激监狱里的员工对他的帮助。
EN: This inmate is grateful for the assistance provided by the prison staff.

ZH: 偷窃是一个常见的犯罪行为，导致很多人进入监狱。
EN: Theft is a common criminal act that lands many people in prison.

ZH: 我希望监狱能够提供更好的教育和康复项目。
EN: I hope that prisons can provide better education and rehabilitation programs.
